ny of the emission properties\nas propagation effects in a non-dipolar magnetic field configuration where\nemission from different multipole components is observed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 14 Feb 2007 01:21:11 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 21 Feb 2007 23:58:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-11-26"}
